#: 59182-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "[He croaks, his voice soft and quiet]... Good to see you again, comrade. Enjoying your freedom, I hope?"
msgstr "[他呱呱叫，聲音溫柔安靜] ......很高興見到你，同志。我希望享受你的自由嗎？"

#. Id: 59189-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (59182-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Grey Talk To (locked)
#. Id: 61591-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (61593-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Grey talk to join
#: 59189-Dialogue.mod:0 61591-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "I want to join the Anti-Slavers."
msgstr "我想加入反奴隸。"

#. Id: 59190-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 2.0
#. -- Parent line: 1 (59189-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Grey Talk To (locked)
#: 59190-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Only a fool denies allies amidst war. So why do you want to join the Anti-Slavers?"
msgstr "只有傻瓜否認戰爭中的盟友。那麼你為什麼要加入反奴隸呢？"

#. Id: 59197-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (59190-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Grey Talk To (locked)
#. Id: 61608-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (61600-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Grey talk to join
#: 59197-Dialogue.mod:0 61608-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Because I want to fight for freedom and peace."
msgstr "因為我想為自由與和平而戰。"

#. Id: 59200-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.0
#. -- Parent line: 3 (59197-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Grey Talk To (locked)
#. Id: 61611-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 6.0
#. -- Parent line: 5 (61608-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Grey talk to join
#: 59200-Dialogue.mod:0 61611-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Freedom is a beautiful thing, isn't it, comrade? But the road to it is not so beautiful..."
msgstr "自由是美好的事，不是嗎，同志？但通往它的道路並不那麼美麗......"

#. Id: 59205-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 6.0
#. -- Parent line: 5 (59203-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Grey Talk To (locked)
#. Id: 61616-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 8.0
#. -- Parent line: 7 (61612-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Grey talk to join
#: 59205-Dialogue.mod:0 61616-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Sign me up."
msgstr "註冊我"

#. Id: 59198-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (59190-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Grey Talk To (locked)
#. Id: 61609-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (61600-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Grey talk to join
#: 59198-Dialogue.mod:0 61609-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Because I want to stick it to the nobles."
msgstr "因為我想把它堅持到貴族身上。"

#. Id: 59204-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.0
#. -- Parent line: 3 (59198-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Grey Talk To (locked)
#. Id: 61613-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 6.0
#. -- Parent line: 5 (61609-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Grey talk to join
#: 59204-Dialogue.mod:0 61613-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Hate is a powerful motivator, isn't it comrade? But it can also cloud our judgement...."
msgstr "仇恨是一個強大的動力，是不是同志？但它也可以掩蓋我們的判斷......"

#. Id: 59199-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (59190-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Grey Talk To (locked)
#. Id: 61610-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (61600-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Grey talk to join
#: 59199-Dialogue.mod:0 61610-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Because I was a slave once."
msgstr "因為我曾經是奴隸。"

#. Id: 59286-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.0
#. -- Parent line: 3 (59199-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Grey Talk To (locked)
#. Id: 61615-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 6.0
#. -- Parent line: 5 (61610-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Grey talk to join
#: 59286-Dialogue.mod:0 61615-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "That makes you one of the lucky few survivors, comrade. But think hard how you want to spend your newfound freedom before you throw it away again..."
msgstr "這使你成為幸運的少數倖存者之一，同志。但是，在你再次把它扔掉之前，想一想你是如何花費新發現的自由的......"

#. Id: 59289-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (59182-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Grey Talk To (locked)
#. Id: 61592-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (61587-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Grey talk to join
#: 59289-Dialogue.mod:0 61592-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Nevermind. I've no business with you."
msgstr "沒關係。我和你沒關係。"
